<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When an Zend_Service_Amazon_S3 is created and makes use of the default secret and access keys, the signature is invalid.</p>

<p>Solution:
Change line 107:
        if (!$secret_key) {
            $secret_key = self::$default_accessKey;
        }</p>

<p>to</p>

<pre><code>   if (!$secret_key) {
        $secret_key = self::$default_secretKey;
    }
</code></pre>

